{"tid":2025604,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拒批警匿名 官：不能常規化","createTime":"2020-05-20T10:59:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T11:19:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"833adc687fa2f095bb119bbc82de0a2874b4bc8c","tid":2025604,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T10:59:11.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200520/XMUWVGBY3XCX42GRTWCBFMOCTE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200520%2FXMUWVGBY3XCX42GRTWCBFMOCTE%2F&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krHhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=af830999\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200520%2FXMUWVGBY3XCX42GRTWCBFMOCTE%2F&h=81796ec6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200520/XMUWVGBY3XCX42GRTWCBFMOCTE/</a><br />\n<br />\n拒批警匿名 官：不能常規化<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200520/large/1589920104_4e9f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200520%2Flarge%2F1589920104_4e9f.jpg&h=6edaea1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】健身教練被指去年10月在將軍澳襲擊警長，控方早前申請將案中警長匿名，昨在九龍城法院處理。署理主任裁判官徐綺薇最終拒絕匿名申請，指高等法院的禁制令生效後，警員被起底個案已大幅回落，控方亦未能說明警長如何受驚，認為不應將匿名常規化。<br />\n<br />\n被告吳智晉（22歲，圖）否認於去年10月7日襲警，控罪原指他在博愛醫院八十週年鄧英喜中學外，襲擊警長A，現改為警長黃成輝。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n辯方：因此受驚違市民期望<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n辯方反對匿名申請，認為高院去年發出的禁制令及現行法例，已足以保護警長A。<br />\n。。。。。。。。。<br />\n禁止公開警長的編號並保密其身份，會令新聞報道變得抽象空洞，損害公眾利益。<br />\n<br />\n徐官指法庭須獨立考慮每宗個案是否有保護申請人身份的足夠理據，否則會將匿名常規化，最終拒絕批出匿名令。<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n案件7月8日開審。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KTCC413/20"},{"pid":"a4a57cccbd5d4bfa8cae82805ed1733eca1462a7","tid":2025604,"uid":288048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T11:05:19.000Z","msg":"叫旺才"},{"pid":"ad41484fbfa34c05c7643d1b052778d4b10872bd","tid":2025604,"uid":127929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T11:15:30.000Z","msg":"黃成輝叫雞唔找數驚比黑社會揾上門?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f9860954d5fe5b4fd88c27983ddc2b7c81c8eb0","tid":2025604,"uid":37869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T11:19:11.000Z","msg":"法官：我唔可以匿名 你都唔可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d055b532312c577f4fe6d8e990e25abb3779cf60","tid":2025604,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T11:19:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}